<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"/>
<title>ML Business Lab — Complete AI & ML Curriculum</title>
<meta name="description" content="The world's most comprehensive free ML & AI curriculum for business professionals. 20 modules · 104 lessons · Zero prerequisites."/>
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --purple:#7C3AED;--purple-light:#F5F3FF;--purple-mid:#6D28D9;--purple-dark:#4C1D95;
  --teal:#0F766E;--teal-light:#F0FDFA;--teal-mid:#0D9488;--teal-dark:#134E4A;
  --amber:#B45309;--amber-light:#FFFBEB;--amber-mid:#D97706;--amber-dark:#78350F;
  --blue:#1D4ED8;--blue-light:#EFF6FF;--blue-mid:#2563EB;--blue-dark:#1E3A8A;
  --bg:#F8F8F8;--surface:#FFFFFF;--border:#E5E7EB;
  --text:#111827;--text2:#6B7280;--text3:#9CA3AF;
}
body{font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);min-height:100vh}
body.dark{--bg:#0D0D0D;--surface:#1A1A1A;--border:#2A2A2A;--text:#F9FAFB;--text2:#9CA3AF;--text3:#6B7280}

/* NAV */
nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;background:var(--surface);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);padding:0 1.5rem;height:58px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.nav-logo{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7C3AED,#4F46E5);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:800;font-size:12px;flex-shrink:0}
.nav-brand{flex:1}
.nav-brand h1{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.1}
.nav-brand p{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2)}
.nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.progress-pill{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 12px 4px 8px}
.progress-track{width:60px;height:5px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--border);overflow:hidden}
.progress-fill{height:100%;background:#7C3AED;border-radius:3px;transition:width .4s}
.progress-pct{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#7C3AED}
.btn-dark{background:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:4px 10px;cursor:pointer;font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);font-family:inherit}
.btn-yt{background:#DC2626;color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:5px 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-family:inherit}

/* LAYOUT */
.layout{display:flex;min-height:calc(100vh - 58px)}
main{flex:1;padding:1.5rem;min-width:0;transition:all .3s}
aside{width:420px;flex-shrink:0;height:calc(100vh - 58px);position:sticky;top:58px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--surface);border-left:1px solid var(--border);transition:all .3s}

/* HERO */
.hero{border-radius:16px;padding:1.75rem 2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4338CA 0%,#7C3AED 55%,#A21CAF 100%);color:#fff;margin-bottom:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-blob1{position:absolute;top:-30px;right:-30px;width:220px;height:220px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}
.hero-blob2{position:absolute;bottom:-50px;right:80px;width:180px;height:180px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
.hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:1}
.hero-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;opacity:.75;margin-bottom:8px}
.hero h2{font-size:clamp(18px,3.5vw,30px);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.2}
.hero p{font-size:13px;opacity:.85;margin:0 0 1.25rem;max-width:500px;line-height:1.65}
.hero-stats{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hero-stat{background:rgba(255,255,255,.15);border-radius:10px;padding:8px 14px;text-align:center;min-width:56px}
.hero-stat-n{font-size:18px;font-weight:800;line-height:1}
.hero-stat-l{font-size:10px;opacity:.8;margin-top:2px}

/* CONTROLS */
.search-input{width:100%;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:10px;outline:none;font-family:inherit}
.search-input:focus{border-color:#7C3AED;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px #7C3AED22}
.phase-tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1.25rem}
.ptab{padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;transition:all .15s;font-family:inherit}
.ptab.off{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text2)}
.ptab.off:hover{background:var(--border)}

/* PROGRESS BAR */
.overall-progress{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.op-bar-wrap{flex:1;min-width:140px}
.op-label{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.05em}
.op-bar{height:8px;background:var(--border);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.op-fill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#7C3AED,#4F46E5);border-radius:4px;transition:width .4s}
.op-count{text-align:right}
.op-num{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#7C3AED;line-height:1}
.op-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2)}
.btn-reset{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);background:none;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:6px;padding:4px 10px;cursor:pointer;font-family:inherit}

/* PHASE */
.phase-block{margin-bottom:2rem}
.phase-header{border-radius:14px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;border:1px solid}
.ph-icon{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;color:#fff}
.ph-info{flex:1}
.ph-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:2px}
.ph-desc{font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:8px;opacity:.8}
.ph-meta{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ph-meta-text{font-size:11px;font-weight:600}
.ph-mini-bar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.ph-mini-track{width:70px;height:4px;border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.ph-mini-fill{height:100%;border-radius:2px;transition:width .4s}
.ph-mini-count{font-size:11px;font-weight:600}

/* MODULES GRID */
.modules-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(290px,1fr));gap:10px}
.mod-card{background:var(--surface);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;transition:border-color .15s;border:1.5px solid var(--border)}
.mod-card.open{border-color:var(--purple)}
.mod-body{padding:1rem 1.1rem}
.mod-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:6px}
.mod-num{font-size:10px;color:var(--text2);font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.05em}
.diff-badge{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:10px;margin-left:auto}
.mod-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px;line-height:1.3;color:var(--text)}
.mod-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.55;margin-bottom:10px}
.mod-footer{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.mod-count{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2)}
.mod-done{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#7C3AED}
.btn-expand{margin-left:auto;font-size:12px;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-weight:700;padding:0;font-family:inherit;transition:color .15s}

/* LESSONS */
.lessons-panel{border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.lesson-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:8px 1.1rem;border-bottom:1px solid;transition:background .1s;cursor:pointer}
.lesson-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.lesson-row.active{background:#F5F3FF}
body.dark .lesson-row.active{background:#1C1427}
.lesson-check{width:18px;height:18px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s;font-size:9px;color:#fff;font-weight:800}
.lesson-check.done{background:#7C3AED;border-color:#7C3AED}
.lesson-info{flex:1;min-width:0}
.lesson-title{font-size:12.5px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.3;color:var(--text);transition:all .15s}
.lesson-title.done{color:var(--text2);text-decoration:line-through}
.lesson-dur{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:1px}
.btn-script{flex-shrink:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;border:1.5px solid;transition:all .15s;white-space:nowrap;font-family:inherit}

/* SIDEBAR */
.sidebar-header{padding:1rem 1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px}
.sidebar-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:4px;color:var(--text2)}
.sidebar-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;color:var(--text)}
.sidebar-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);margin-top:2px}
.btn-close{background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:22px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1;padding:0 2px;margin-left:auto;font-family:inherit}
.sidebar-body{flex:1;overflow:auto;padding:1.25rem}
.sidebar-empty{text-align:center;padding-top:2.5rem;color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;line-height:1.8}
.sidebar-empty-icon{font-size:36px;opacity:.3;margin-bottom:12px}
.loading-wrap{text-align:center;padding-top:2.5rem}
.loading-icon{font-size:32px;opacity:.4;margin-bottom:14px;animation:spin 2s linear infinite;display:inline-block}
.loading-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:6px}
.loading-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7}
.dots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:5px;margin-top:16px}
.dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:#7C3AED}
.script-content{font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.9;white-space:pre-wrap;color:var(--text)}
.script-actions{margin-top:1.5rem;display:flex;gap:8px}
.btn-copy{flex:1;padding:9px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;background:#7C3AED;color:#fff;border:none;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;font-family:inherit}
.btn-regen{flex:1;padding:9px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;background:none;border:1px solid var(--border);font-size:12px;color:var(--text);font-family:inherit}

/* FOOTER */
.footer{margin-top:2rem;padding:1.5rem;background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;text-align:center}
.footer h3{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px}
.footer p{font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:12px;line-height:1.6}

/* EMPTY */
.no-results{text-align:center;padding:3rem;color:var(--text2);font-size:14px}

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
@keyframes dot-pulse{0%,100%{opacity:.25;transform:scale(.8)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.15)}}
.dot:nth-child(1){animation:dot-pulse 1.2s .0s infinite}
.dot:nth-child(2){animation:dot-pulse 1.2s .2s infinite}
.dot:nth-child(3){animation:dot-pulse 1.2s .4s infinite}

/* SCROLLBAR */
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#D1D5DB;border-radius:2px}
body.dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:#4B5563}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:768px){
  aside{display:none}
  .modal-overlay{display:flex!important}
  .nav-right .progress-pill{display:none}
}

/* MOBILE MODAL */
.modal-overlay{display:none;position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:500;background:rgba(0,0,0,.6);align-items:flex-end}
.modal-sheet{background:var(--surface);border-radius:16px 16px 0 0;width:100%;max-height:85vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.modal-header{padding:1rem 1.25rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px}
.modal-body{flex:1;overflow:auto;padding:1.25rem}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">ML</div>
  <div class="nav-brand">
    <h1>ML Business Lab</h1>
    <p>Prof. ML · CS · MSc Data Science · PhD Machine Learning &amp; AI</p>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-right">
    <div class="progress-pill">
      <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" id="navProg" style="width:0%"></div></div>
      <span class="progress-pct" id="navPct">0%</span>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-dark" onclick="toggleDark()">◐ Dark</button>
    <a class="btn-yt" href="https://youtube.com/@MLBusinessLab" target="_blank">▶ Subscribe</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="layout">
  <!-- MAIN -->
  <main id="mainContent">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-blob1"></div>
      <div class="hero-blob2"></div>
      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-label">ML BUSINESS LAB · PROFESSOR EDITION · THE WORLD'S MOST COMPREHENSIVE FREE ML & AI CURRICULUM</div>
        <h2>From Math Concepts to Business Insights</h2>
        <p>Zero prerequisites. 20 modules. 104 lessons. 44 weeks. Every lesson clickable, every production script AI-generatable in one click. Built for business professionals who want to truly understand and use machine learning.</p>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">4</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Phases</div></div>
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">20</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Modules</div></div>
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">104</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Lessons</div></div>
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">44wk</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Full course</div></div>
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">0</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Prerequisites</div></div>
          <div class="hero-stat"><div class="hero-stat-n">Free</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Always</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SEARCH -->
    <input class="search-input" id="searchInput" placeholder="🔍  Search all 104 lessons, modules and topics..." oninput="render()"/>

    <!-- PHASE TABS -->
    <div class="phase-tabs" id="phaseTabs"></div>

    <!-- OVERALL PROGRESS -->
    <div class="overall-progress">
      <div class="op-bar-wrap">
        <div class="op-label">YOUR OVERALL PROGRESS</div>
        <div class="op-bar"><div class="op-fill" id="opFill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="op-count">
        <div class="op-num" id="opNum">0</div>
        <div class="op-sub" id="opSub">of 104 lessons complete</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-reset" onclick="resetProgress()">Reset</button>
    </div>

    <!-- CURRICULUM -->
    <div id="curriculumContainer"></div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="footer">
      <h3>ML Business Lab</h3>
      <p>The world's most comprehensive free ML &amp; AI curriculum for business professionals.<br/>
      Prof. ML · BSc Computer Science · MSc Data Science, Machine Learning &amp; AI · PhD Machine Learning &amp; AI</p>
      <a class="btn-yt" href="https://youtube.com/@MLBusinessLab" target="_blank" style="display:inline-flex">▶ Subscribe on YouTube</a>
    </div>

  </main>

  <!-- DESKTOP SIDEBAR -->
  <aside id="desktopSidebar">
    <div class="sidebar-header">
      <div style="flex:1">
        <div class="sidebar-label">AI LESSON SCRIPT GENERATOR</div>
        <div class="sidebar-title" id="sidebarTitle">Select any lesson</div>
        <div class="sidebar-sub" id="sidebarSub">Click "Script ↗" on any lesson to generate</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-close" onclick="closeSidebar()">×</button>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-body" id="sidebarBody">
      <div class="sidebar-empty">
        <div class="sidebar-empty-icon">📝</div>
        <strong>AI Script Generator</strong><br/><br/>
        Click the <strong>Script ↗</strong> button on any lesson below to instantly generate a full MIT-style production script.<br/><br/>
        <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)">Includes: timed segments · stage directions · spoken dialogue · graphics brief · B-roll notes · CTA</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>
</div>

<!-- MOBILE MODAL -->
<div class="modal-overlay" id="mobileModal" onclick="closeMobileModal(event)">
  <div class="modal-sheet">
    <div class="modal-header">
      <div style="flex:1">
        <div class="sidebar-label">AI LESSON SCRIPT GENERATOR</div>
        <div class="sidebar-title" id="modalTitle">Lesson</div>
        <div class="sidebar-sub" id="modalSub"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-close" onclick="document.getElementById('mobileModal').style.display='none'">×</button>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body" id="modalBody"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// CURRICULUM DATA
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
const CURRICULUM = [
  {
    id:'p1',phase:1,label:'Phase 1',title:'Absolute Foundations',
    color:'#7C3AED',light:'#F5F3FF',border:'#DDD6FE',dark:'#4C1D95',mid:'#6D28D9',
    weeks:'Weeks 1–8',totalVideos:26,icon:'∑',
    desc:'Zero to ready. Math, statistics, Python and data — built for someone who has never written a line of code or opened a spreadsheet for analysis. No jargon. No shortcuts. Just clear, permanent understanding.',
    modules:[
      {id:'m1',num:'01',title:'What Is Machine Learning?',diff:'Beginner',videos:3,
       desc:'The big picture. Understand what ML is, where it lives in the world, and why it matters — with zero jargon and three examples you experienced today without realising it.',
       lessons:[
         {n:1,title:'What is machine learning? (plain English)',dur:'10 min',prompt:'Write a full MIT-style YouTube production script for ML Business Lab — Module 1 Video 1: What Is Machine Learning? Include: (1) cold open hook 30s, (2) who this channel is for 90s, (3) the core definition with 2 analogies 3min, (4) 3 real-world examples with b-roll notes 2min, (5) the three types overview 90s, (6) channel roadmap 60s, (7) close + CTA 60s. Include stage directions in [brackets], timing labels, key graphic descriptions. Beginner audience. Warm, authoritative MIT tone.'},
         {n:2,title:'Traditional programming vs machine learning',dur:'9 min',prompt:'Write a full MIT-style YouTube production script for ML Business Lab — Module 1 Video 2: Traditional Programming vs Machine Learning. Cover: the paradigm flip (Input+Rules=Output vs Input+Output=Rules), the cookbook and chef analogy, tax software vs spam filter examples, the side-by-side comparison table. Include animated graphic briefs, stage directions, timing, spoken dialogue samples.'},
         {n:3,title:'Where you already use ML every day',dur:'9 min',prompt:'Write a full MIT-style YouTube production script for ML Business Lab — Module 1 Video 3: Where You Already Use ML Every Day. Cover invisible ML: Spotify, Gmail spam, fraud alerts, face unlock, Amazon recommendations, Google Maps ETA, autocomplete. Show how each one works at a conceptual level. Engaging, eye-opening tone.'},
       ]},
      {id:'m2',num:'02',title:'Math Essentials — No Panic',diff:'Beginner',videos:6,
       desc:'The minimum math you actually need for ML. Made visual and intuitive. If you passed secondary school maths, you have everything required.',
       lessons:[
         {n:1,title:'What is a function? (and why ML is full of them)',dur:'10 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V1 — What is a Function for ML. Intuition first, equation second. Connect to ML throughout.'},
         {n:2,title:'Slopes, rates of change and gradient intuition',dur:'11 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V2 — Slopes and Gradient Intuition. Seed the concept of gradient descent. Visual, no calculus panic.'},
         {n:3,title:'Vectors: lists of numbers that mean something',dur:'9 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V3 — Vectors Explained Visually. From arrays to geometry, distance and similarity.'},
         {n:4,title:'Matrices: the language of data',dur:'10 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V4 — Matrices for ML. Rows, columns, transformations, dot products made visual.'},
         {n:5,title:'Logarithms without the trauma',dur:'8 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V5 — Logarithms for ML. Why ML loves log, log loss, entropy — all intuitive.'},
         {n:6,title:'Mini-project: visualising math with Python',dur:'14 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M2V6 — Visualising Math with Python. First hands-on code, matplotlib plots of all concepts covered.'},
       ]},
      {id:'m3',num:'03',title:'Statistics for ML — The Real Stuff',diff:'Beginner',videos:7,
       desc:'Statistics is the language ML speaks. Mean, distributions, probability, Bayes — all connected to data you will actually use in business decisions.',
       lessons:[
         {n:1,title:'Mean, median, mode — and when each one lies',dur:'9 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V1 — Mean Median Mode for ML. When each measure misleads and why it matters.'},
         {n:2,title:'Variance and standard deviation, visually',dur:'10 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V2 — Variance and Standard Deviation. Spread, bell curves, and why ML cares.'},
         {n:3,title:'Probability from scratch',dur:'11 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V3 — Probability from Scratch. Coins, cards, conditional probability, connecting to ML predictions.'},
         {n:4,title:'Probability distributions: normal, binomial, Poisson',dur:'10 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V4 — Probability Distributions for ML. The shapes data takes, with business examples.'},
         {n:5,title:'Correlation vs causation — the most important distinction',dur:'9 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V5 — Correlation vs Causation. Business examples, spurious correlations, why this matters in ML.'},
         {n:6,title:'Bayes theorem in plain English',dur:'12 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V6 — Bayes Theorem Plain English. Medical tests, spam filters, Bayesian thinking for business.'},
         {n:7,title:'Stats project: exploring a real business dataset',dur:'16 min',prompt:'Write full lesson script: ML Business Lab M3V7 — Stats Mini Project Real Dataset. Full EDA with descriptive stats in Python, business insights.'},
       ]},
      {id:'m4',num:'04',title:'Python for Data Science — From Zero',diff:'Beginner',videos:10,
       desc:'Your first line of code today. From hello world to manipulating real datasets — every step explained, nothing assumed.',
       lessons:[
